parameters:
\n<Deorc>"Hey! Where the hell do you think you're going! Let me out
of here!"

\n<Deorc>"You bastards, locking me up in a place like this! You won't
get away with this for free!"
\n<Deorc>"Hey! Are you listening to me, hey!!"
\n<Deorc>"Damn it... I can't end up in a place like this..."

\n<???>"It's not a hallucination. You are perfectly sane. The
picture of health."

\n<???>"...Somehow, this feels nostalgic. History does have a way
of repeating itself, doesn't it?"
\n<Deorc>"Who the hell are you!? Where did you come from!?"

\n<???>"Where from... Well, that would take some time to explain.
For now, can you just not worry about it?"

\n<Deorc>"Hah...? What do you mean 'don't worry about it', don't mess
with me!"

\n<???>"...Please don't make such a fuss. I understand you're
irritated, but raising your voice won't help us move forward
with the conversation."

\n<???>"You're not the brightest, but you're shrewd. First, shut
that noisy mouth of yours and listen to what I have to say."
\n<Deorc>"What the hell are you talking about..."

\n<???>"Please don't be so wary. I've come here because I have a
request for you."
\n<???>"Yes. But it's nothing to be so tense about."

\n<???>"Will you listen to my story? As a token of our new
acquaintance, I'll set you free."

As the woman waved her finger, the ropes binding Deorc were
easily untied.

\n<???>"Nfufu... If you're surprised by just that, you won't last
long from here on out."

The woman chuckled and embraced her own body with a
seductive gesture.

\n<???>"Frustrating. Frustrating. Frustrating... I understand that
feeling very well."

\n<???>"Having one's purpose crushed midway is an unbearable
torment."

\n<???>"...You see, I'm also irritated. Just like you, very...
very, very..."
\n<???>"Very, very, very, very, very, very, very, very..."

\n<???>"That's why let's take revenge together. On those who
irritate us. On those we dislike. Let's exact vengeance."

\n<???>"I'll lend you a hand. Just entrust yourself to me. Then,
I'll lend you power."

\n<???>"I'll transform your vengeful desires burning for revenge
into the power of violence."

\n<Deorc>"--Haha! After all that grand talk, what nonsense are you
spouting... Just empty words when your mouth opens."

\n<Deorc>"Due to my line of work, I meet guys like you all the time.
Want to know what they're called? Swindlers, that's what
they're called, swindlers. Remember that well."

\n<Deorc>"You also used some kind of magic trick to untie the ropes
earlier, didn't you? Resorting to such petty tricks."

\n<Deorc>"I don't know what you're plotting, but I don't have time to
play your silly games."

\n<Deorc>"That guy... Roselitte! She's looking all smug, laughing at
me. I'll make her regret it for sure!"

\n<Deorc>"And that sister too, Ameria! With her around, a fortune is
within reach! This time I'll definitely make a killing!"
\n<Deorc>"And I... I will, this time for sure...!"
\n<Deorc>"What the... why all of a sudden..."

\n<??>"...Nice. Fate has a strange way of bringing people
together."

\n<??>"If it's you, surely you can weave the ideal story that
child desires."

\n<??>"I won't let you go alone. You will listen to what I have to
say."

\n<??>"Are you irritated? Do you deeply wish to relieve that
frustration from the bottom of your heart?"

\n<Deorc>"Of course I'm pissed off! I'll show the Empire what I'm
made of!"

\n<??>"Do you want women? Money? Violence? Don't you want to
satisfy your parched desires to your heart's content?"

\n<??>"Just entrust yourself to me. If you do, I will grant your
wishes.... And then--"

\n<??>"And then, you will become someone who fulfills the wishes
of those who seek them."
\n<Begieade>"My name is Begieade.... Now, take me into your hands."
